          <Vi>Sự giữ gìn vệ sinh; các biện pháp vệ sinh</Vi>
          <En>The practice of keeping oneself and one’s surroundings clean to prevent disease.</En>
          <Example>Good hygiene is essential to avoid spreading infections, especially in hospitals.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
